{"tid":826413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[RIP]貼一下陪伴你地成長，前日捱唔過山竹嘅老樹","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:44:04.000Z","uid":22633,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6458bd6b86adaeea8ef0f0225da7cc4b18d1b2","tid":826413,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/161727_bbaee0da790e9d7e319f2514315cb53b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F161727_bbaee0da790e9d7e319f2514315cb53b.png&h=493fed13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個喺度住左廿年，估唔到你都捱唔住，<br />\n雖然搬走左好多年，但係每次經過都有好多畫面，<br />\n記起好多個夏天喺你下面經過，你都幫我擋一擋太陽，再見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貼嘅唔單止係一碌斷樹，仲係我地逝去時光嘅一部分，我地嘅成長有你分享過，真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9392a3c673df7247d150f22c2b1ca9adf273be7e","tid":826413,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"睇到都眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dada695f015e91c79065d7413f4876ce6bd4afa1","tid":826413,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkedcity.net/cms_files/cms-funpost/1-1000/2abd1d585e2b5bd595058f98aaaa882f340/榕樹03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkedcity.net%2Fcms_files%2Fcms-funpost%2F1-1000%2F2abd1d585e2b5bd595058f98aaaa882f340%2F%E6%A6%95%E6%A8%B903.jpg&h=7bd39f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n榕樹要靠氣根去支撐個樹冠<br />\n係巿區根本冇機會畀啲氣根生落泥度<br />\n時間一長棵樹生得越黎越高<br />\n但係又冇足夠承托<br />\n所以係巿區一棵棵百年老樹就變成計時炸彈"}]}